                            </div>
                            <div class="col-3">
                                <strong>–í–∏–∫–æ–Ω–∞–Ω–æ:</strong>
                                <t t-esc="completedTodos"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-3">
                                <strong>–ü—Ä–æ–≥—Ä–µ—Å:</strong>
